name: WalkedtheDog
0:
”Alexa, open walked the dog”
”Alexa, ask walked the dog how long ago did the dog walk”
”Alexa, ask walked the dog did the dog have her walk already?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: walked the dog
des:
Living with multiple roommates or with a big family, it sometimes gets difficult to know if the dog went of its walk already. This skill helps you to keep better track of this. 

Just report a walk saying "I just walked the dog" and if someone else is interested in knowing when was the dog walked they can just ask "was the dog out already?"
